name: Oracles of the Floating Note
description: Receiving aid from the Mohoe in a time of great need, the Oracles of the Floating Note were left with a deep seated gratitude towards the Mohoe. They're also known for their captivating music that seems to overwhelm listeners with ecstasy. Now residing atop the oasis crabs of Kathoon, they look towards the future with a glint in their eye. Their future is bright. The only question: what comes next?
